---
title: Spiced Beef Skewer Rice Bowls with Tomato Cucumber Salad, Lemony Hummus & Toasted Pitas
description: We love a rice bowl! Street-food-fave beef skewers are spiced up with our aromatic, earthy shawarma spice blend, roasted to perfection and then served atop fragrant, fluffy rice. And to tick all of the boxes, our chefs added a crunchy, fresh tomato-cuke salad, a dollop of lemony hummus, and toasty whole wheat pitas for scooping or serving alongside. You do you!
